            </did>
            <scopecontent id="aspace_ff481776d8854d0f0cb74da5ca253cb9">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>This series is arranged according to type of record: ledger, daybooks, account books, bills and miscellaneous.</p>
               <p>Miscellaneous contains promissory notes, premium notes, receipts, an arithmetic books and a death certificate.</p>
               <p>Jabez Turner Potter's general bills are in chronological order at the beginning of the section with his specific bills chronologically arranged next. These are followed by Blakeslee bills and miscellaneous.</p>
            </scopecontent>
